{"tid":1660943,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"戴口罩用唔到Face ID？其實係得㗎！","createTime":"2019-10-17T23:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T05:58:32.000Z","uid":32017,"like":5,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1b50c473652fa23d6124dc6749e2a7e26180c189","tid":1660943,"uid":32017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:28:28.000Z","msg":"戴口罩用唔到Face ID？其實係得㗎！<br />\n<br />\nApple曾經解釋過Face ID會透過Machine Learning 去學習你本人每天的變化...👱🏻&zwj;♂️🧔🏻<br />\n<br />\n我而家訓練到部iPhone不論我戴口罩、朝早鼻敏感搵紙巾塞鼻遮蓋下半邊臉，佢都準確無誤認到我本人為我即時解鎖... 😀👍🏻👍🏻<br />\n<br />\n所以訓練成功後就算你份工需要帶口罩工作，都可以放心使用Face ID 🤗<br />\n<br />\n好！事不宜遲...等我講解下步驟先👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n首先你要有部有Face ID功能嘅iPhone (廢話👻)，戴上口罩之後持續去嘗試解鎖，當解鎖失敗後就輸入密碼解鎖🔓<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不停反覆嘗試大約20-30次...</strong><br />\n<br />\n如是者你就會發現神奇的事發生了...你唔再需要除口罩或用密碼都能透過Face ID解到鎖。<br />\n<br />\n但如果無戴口罩一排再戴番，它就會還原最初，到時你就要再做多次以上步驟先可以。<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到需要發夢戴口罩的各位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"14aac1ef1ae89826eef4813c5c841a4f5ed48287","tid":1660943,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:29:35.000Z","msg":"樓主的帖文真有用<br />\n謝謝分享"},{"pid":"16206759d0ee1286944531793e939bfc33f7969d","tid":1660943,"uid":37408,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"發夢就disable face id先啦"},{"pid":"d82cc2096d56a2e1613c20e45077df52878f2aab","tid":1660943,"uid":267172,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"發夢唔好開Faceid"},{"pid":"c393cb453296c6faa282b27cb73f523289d97ce4","tid":1660943,"uid":321123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:43:44.000Z","msg":"除口罩就唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ea593c0ebd7ac6845ca966a36a37e46a7e8012","tid":1660943,"uid":59955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c393cb453296c6faa282b27